62273996.text: "It was previously showed that ectopically expressed, constitutively active chimeras between Wnt8 and Fz1 or overexpression of Wnt10b in pre-adipocytes and MSCs increased the levels of beta-catenin and inhibited adipogenesis by blocking the induction of the key transcription factors PPARG and CEBPA [XREF_BIBR]."
